-- GM shares rise after restructuring news
-- 
-- Tue Jul 15, 2008 8:52am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/15/us-shares-gm-idUSL1531222020080715

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of General Motors Corp rose 2.8 percent to $9.65 before the bell on Tuesday, after the automaker said it would cut jobs and raise liquidity by $15 billion.  

 (Reporting by Wall Street newsdesk)